and is released under the GNU General Public License v2.0, matching the
licence of the WF engine itself.

  https://www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/gpl-2.0.html

This licence applies to the metapackage source (packages/*/DEBIAN/control),
the helper scripts (scripts/*.sh), the aptly configuration, and the
GitHub Actions workflows.

Upstream packages we repackage and redistribute via this repo keep their
original licences. Each repackaged .deb embeds the upstream LICENSE / COPYING
under /usr/share/doc/<package>/. A roll-up summary lives in
LICENSES-VENDORED.md (added once we ship the first vendored upstream pkg).
